@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5

actor Developer
participant "Build Tool" as Build
database "Data Source" as Data
participant "Server / CDN" as CDN

Developer -> Build ++ : trigger build
Build -> Data : fetch content / data
Data --> Build : data
Build -> Build : generate static HTML files
Build -> CDN : deploy static files
Build --> Developer --
@enduml
